nodes.text: Carolyn Lee Hennesy (born June 10, 1962) is an American actress who voiced General Leia Organa in LEGO Star Wars: All-Stars and Star Wars Resistance. She also portrayed Domine Lithe in the 2019 movie Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. Hennesy is known for playing Diane Miller on General Hospital and playing recurring roles on TV series such as Dawson's Creek, Cougar Town, Revenge, Jessie and The Bay.
